@startuml
title Outbox Event Lifecycle

[*] --> NEW : business tx committed

NEW --> PUBLISHED : publish success
NEW --> FAILED : publish failure

FAILED --> PUBLISHED : retry success
FAILED --> FAILED : retry failure and retryCount < maxRetries
FAILED --> FATAL : retry failure and retryCount >= maxRetries

PUBLISHED --> [*]
FATAL --> [*]

@enduml
